result.formatted_address: 8-10 Queen's Rd E, Admiralty, Hong Kong
result.name: MANA! StarStreet

reviews.text: I like the wrap which you can customize your own ingredient. The quality of the food is good - all fresh and clean. The music is like ...i think it's called reggae music. The atmostphere is nice also, suite for group of friends, family. I dont think they allow pet inside the store.

This is the second time now in recent times that I’ve been to mana and been disappointed. I ordered a wrap and to my disappointment it was fairly empty. The wraps used to be consistently full with the toppings that you order, to the point where I would struggle to eat a full wrap. On my last two visits, the wraps were so empty and thin. Probably won’t go back again for a wrap since the wraps have become so stingy.
Mediocre staff, good food and amazing environment!
